Class ComparatorColumn<T>

com.jsql.view.swing.table.ComparatorColumn<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparator<T>
public class ComparatorColumn<T> extends Object implements Comparator<T>
Comparator for table column values ; column with only int data is sorted like 3 lt 20 lt 100, column with string will sort like 100 gt 20 gt 3 gt a.
